title: Guantes, Guantes Maestros
description: Los nuevos guantes de Owen hacen que sea muy hábil en todo. Pero su grandeza tiene un precio.

title: Huggbees
description: The Brain teams up with The Lobe, so the Titans enlist the help of Freakazoid to stop them.

title: Efecto Entrega
description: Unikitty y su banda pidieron una deliciosa comida tailandesa para la cena. Por desgracia, la espera para la entrega se está haciendo demasiado larga y hasta el tiempo parece pasar más lento. En un esfuerzo por conseguir la comida más rápido, la banda utiliza la máquina del tiempo de la Dra. Fox, lo cual causa graves problemas y hiere profundamente los sentimientos del Padre Tiempo.

title: #LosConejosMágicos
description: Cuando Zee le pide a Kara que cuide a sus dos conejitos mágicos, pronto comienzan a multiplicarse y a desatar el caos por toda Metrópolis.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: A Patch of Perturbed Petunias
description: Share fears she's losing her ability as a problem-solver and peacemaker when she can't calm a squabble between a group of Whiffles and a flower bed of Perturbed Petunias. Cheer discovers it's not Share's fault; the Petunias are being secretly manipulated by Bluster's rumor-mongering.

title: And Then There Was Ben
description: Professor Paradox unites the good Bens from across all dimensions to take on Vilgax, Eon, and the evil Bens in the ultimate showdown!

title: Sister Sitter
description: When Blossom and Bubbles get sick, Buttercup volunteers to take care of them for the day.

title: La Dama
description: Los niños descubren que Papá se ha vestido como una mujer para conocer amigos.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Lazer Tag
description: Cuando un villano atrapa a Unikitty y a la banda en su campo de disparos láser, deben derrotar al equipo local o quedar atrapados para siempre.

title: Lie-Ranosaurus Wrecked
description: Owen pretends to be Izzy's pet dinosaur after leading her to believe she dug him up in the school playground.

title: Elly on Ice
description: Pocoyo and Pato are having fun ice-skating. Elly is a great dancer and wants to have a go, but every time she tries she falls over flat on her bottom. Even Whale and Octopus put on a great duet ice-skating routine. Poor Elly is about to give up. But we encourage her to have another go, and Pocoyo and Pato help her to get started. Gradually she gets the hang of it and her confidence increases till she performs an amazing routine and achieves the highest score of the day.

title: Robo Teacher
description: When a substitute teacher fills in for Chef, Duncan thinks it's going to be the best day ever. He's wrong.

title: The Curse of Elmore
description: When Gumball's schoolfriend Leslie finds an old video tape, the creepy mystery of Elmore's ghostly past unfolds. Featuring spooky and hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Inventor Mentor
description: Uncle Grandpa goes to Italy to help a young girl who wants to be a great inventor.

title: El Patron de Oro
description: Llega el Día de San Patricio y, luego de desear convertirse en un duende, Chico Bestia se obsesiona con el oro.

title: The Powerpuff Girls Best Rainy Day Adventure Ever/Just Desserts
description: The Powerpuff Girls Best Rainy Day Adventure Ever: It's raining in Townsville and there is no crime or villainy afoot. So the girls must stay inside and come up with their very own Powerpuff adventure./Just Desserts: The Smith Family is back and they want revenge. Harold, Maryanne and the kids become a super villain team and make it their goal to destroy the perfect Powerpuff family.

title: Appreciation Day
description: By trying to change Benson's opinion of them, Mordecai and Rigby accidentally create lots of work for themselves.

title: Speed of Sound
description: Team Tennyson participates in the inaugural ride of the Sonitrain, the fastest train in the world, but when the conductor turns out to be Lord Decibel, Ben must derail his master plan if he is to save his family and the passengers on board the runaway train.

title: No es Gracioso
description: Cuando se acerca el aniversario de seis meses de amistad, Manzana tiene que encontrar una manera de no perder a su mejor amigo.

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Capullos de Rosa
description: Steven recibe una visita sorpresa de algunos viejos amigos y una introducción aún más sorprendente a algunos nuevos.

title: Bears and the Beanstalk
description: The Bears work as short-order cooks in a giant's diner.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: Beyond the Grotto
description: In pursuit of a runaway Sea Lard, Finn and Jake are led down a whirlpool to a curious new land.

title: Superstar Dan/Awesome Brawlers on Vacation
description: Superstar Dan: The Awesome Brawler's head to Tokyo for the Bakugan Battle League - Tokyo Edition. While Wynton, Shun, Lia and Lightning see the sites, and enjoy the tastes of Japan, Dan, as the Los Volmos Champion, has official Bakugan Battle League duties and obligations that keep him busy./Awesome Brawlers on Vacation: Lia, Lightning, Shun and Wynton explore the sights of Toyko when a rogue Bakugan shows up and rampages. The Awesome Brawlers have to spring into action, rolling out their Bakugan to stop the rogue enemy before any real damage can be done.

title: The Little Mer-Bear
description: In order to live under the sea the Bears must transform into mermaids.

title: Parking Lot
description: Bing's parking his speedy cars but what will Bing do when Charlie wants to play too?

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Elmore's Most Wanted
description: Gumball's dad has been revealed as "Elmore's Most Wanted" - but when the Chief of Police tries to investigate, things do not go according to plan. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Gryffindor v Hufflepuff
description: Dame Helen Mirren hosts the first episode of this epic TV event series. Over 4 episodes the Houses of Hogwarts will do battle to see which team knows the most about the wizarding world, featuring celebrity guests, actors from the original films and more Harry Potter Magic than you could find on a day trip to Diagon Alley. Tonight's match up sees the brave Gryffindors face the loyal Hufflepuffs for a guaranteed place in the grand finale.
originalseriesname: Harry Potter: Hogwarts Tournament of Houses

title: #TrianguloDeOdio
description: Cuando la exnovia de Hal aparece en el partido de bienvenida de la preparatoria Metrópolis y se enfurece por amor, convertida en la villana Star Sapphire, Jessica comienza a cuestionar sus propias tácticas no violentas.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Speed Demon/Mojo Jonesin'
description: Mojo Jonesin':  When the children of Pokey Oaks become envious of the girls' superpowers, a mysterious figure offers them Chemical X. Now, the girls must fight their own classmates who have powers equal to their own./Speed Demon: The girls accidentally fly at the speed of light and when they arrive home, everything has changed. Fifty years have passed and the world has been taken over by Him.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Get Active Dance
description: Mei, Ella, animals and vegetables have a farm active day exercising and organising the farm

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Rose Buds
description: Steven gets a surprise visit from some old friends, and an even more surprising introduction to some new ones.

title: Video Date
description: Panda is an avid e-dater, and when a lovely French woman matches with him and agrees to a video chat date. Panda and his brothers engineer the situation so Panda is able to show the best side of himself on the video chat, even if that side of him is completely exaggerated.

title: Registro Permanente
description: Cuando los Titanes se enseñan sobre ciencia y gramática unos a otros, es como si volvieran a la escuela.

title: Musical Statues
description: Bing gets to choose the game at Amma's Creche, but will his also be the winner?

title: Una sola rosa palida
description: Steven ayuda a Perla a encontrar su teléfono.

title: Baby Brouhaha
description: Overhearing Granny on the phone say she's expecting a baby, Baby Bugs goes into overdrive, revving up the Baby Looney Tunes to prepare to care for an infant.

title: Voleibol
description: Steven está decidido a ayudar a la Perla original de Diamante Rosa para sanar la cicatriz en su rostro.

title: El Horario de Verano Titan
description: Los Titanes están decididos a descubrir qué le sucedió a las dos de la tarde, la hora que se perdió durante el horario de verano.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: The Perfect Fritter
description: Chep has been watching Sushi-Mushi test new compost fritters recipes. When Mush-Mush gets to taste one, he can't believe it: Sushi-Mushi has cooked the perfect fritter. He tells the news to everyone in Mushton and now, all the Mushables want to taste the perfect fritter too! Only problem is the pressure is so high Sushi-Mushi can't remember the recipe anymore.

title: Las Dos Espadas
description: Para escapar de la prisión del Hechicero Calavera, los Ninjas debe convencer a los Munces y a Geckles de que dejen de discutir y trabajen juntos.

title: Pequena Escuela Madre
description: Bienvenidos a la Pequeña Escuela Madre, un lugar en la Tierra donde Gemas de todo el universo pueden aprender a vivir juntas pacíficamente. Pero hay una Gema que se rehúsa a asistir.

title: The Cast
description: After breaking his leg, Robin is confined to his room and spies through a telescope.

title: Unlock the Magic: The Beginning
description: The discovery of an ancient, lost gateway leads the Care Bears on a rescue mission in the Silver Lining, a realm of natural wonders and comical creatures in the clouds beyond the borders of Care-A-Lot. While there, new discoveries expand the mission, challenging Cheer, Grumpy, and the mission team to grow beyond their present abilities and help the denizens of the Silver Lining.

title: Oh Brother, Warehouse Art Thou?
description: Baby Sylvester is overcome with angst because Granny's broken old chair, his favorite napping place, must be replaced by a new, unfamiliar piece of furniture. The other Baby Looney Tunes work together to help turn Sylvester's trepidation into enjoyment during their mammoth furniture-shopping adventure.

title: The Other Fight
description: Eliminated from the Bakugan Battle League, Ajit is airlifted by drone to a massive cargo ship in the middle of Tokyo Bay. Now that he's on board the cargo ship, he must rescue Dan and Drago, and stop whoever is sabotaging the Battle League. Dan and Ajit investigate the mysterious cargo ship that the eliminated brawlers and Bakugan are being held on. Dan races to track down Drago, but along the way runs into a familiar face.

title: Made of Honor
description: Steven has a big surprise for the Crystal Gems.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Peeps
description: Benson gets surveillance cameras to keep track of Mordecai and Rigby on the job.

title: Third Time's a Charm
description: Charmaster returns to exact her revenge on Gwendolyn once and for all.

title: El Trampolin de Hamburguesa
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben encontrar una manera de usar el trampolín de Hamburguesa sin que él se sienta usado.

title: Glove Glove Me Do
description: Owen's newly found gloves make him great at everything. But this greatness comes at a high price.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Money Broom Wizard
description: Can Clarence, Jeff and Sumo manage to have a good time at "Pizza Swamp" Arcade with only one dollar to spend between them? Yes.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Festival de Cine
description: iEs la noche del estreno en el Festival de Cine de Unireino! Todo el mundo está entusiasmado por ver lo que hicieron los amigos, especialmente Richard, que se considera el máximo experto en cine y no puede esperar a destrozar todas las películas de los demás. Pero después de interpretar el papel del crítico, ¿será la película de Rick una obra maestra o un fracaso?

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Presentando a Kevin 11
description: En un encuentro de intercambio local, Ben se interesa en un coleccionable de Luchadores de Sumo. Pero cuando Kevin se apodera del objeto, nuestro héroe debe superar el arma secreta de Kevin para recuperarlo: iun 11º extraterrestre!

title: Cual es tu problema
description: Amatista convence a Steven de que se tome un día libre.

title: The Tooth About Zombies
description: When Gwen's favorite event, the Zombie March, falls on the same day as Noah's nightmare event, dental hygienist check up day, Gwen and Noah find a way to help each other out.

title: Garbage Truck
description: Blippi and TABBS shrink down and fly into a garbage truck where they meet Horace, a singing and dancing fly, who shows them what he loves to eat--garbage!

title: Voo Voo
description: It's breakfast time, and when Bing accidentally spills his Krispos, Voo Voo can help clean it up. But will that be all Voo Voo cleans up?

title: Capture The Flag Part III
description: Craig goes in search of answers, and finds a legend.

title: Flu the Coop
description: Baby Bugs and Baby Daffy decide to team up and unlike the other Baby Looney Tunes, fake having received their annual flu shots at the local clinic. The joke's on them when they awaken on the day of Granny's big party unable to have fun because they both have the flu.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Australia Kangaroo
description: Blippi stumbles across a Kangaroo Crossing sign in Australia and wonders "How high can a kangaroo jump?" His new kangaroo mate Rudy is happy to demonstrate, challenging Blippi to a hopping race around the famous sandstone monolith Uluru. Can Blippi jump as high as a kangaroo?

title: Rain, Rain Go Away
description: After Grumpy's anger sends his belly badge out of control with a thunderstorm that floods a newly-planted Whiffle meadow, he vows to never be grumpy again. Renaming himself "Mr. Happy," he drives everyone crazy with niceness. When the Whiffles desperately need his clouds to make rain and Mr. Happy can't deliver, Cheer and the team must get him back in touch with his inner grump.

title: Twisted Sister/Cover Up
description: Twisted Sister: The girls decide they need some help fighting crime so they create another Powerpuff Girl. But they don't get the combination of sugar, spice and everything nice quite right./Cover Up: Blossom and Bubbles learn that Buttercup has secretly been rubbing a security blanket before every battle to make herself a super fighter. Can the girls convince Buttercup that her strength is within?

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Lady
description: When Gumball and Darwin track a women emerging from their home, they discover her to be a member of a gang of wise-cracking elderly friends. However, as they get closer and closer to her life, they realize they may know her already.

title: Sleeping Dogs/Skunked/Arlo And The Snake
description: Lucas and Findley discover a cake, and they try to keep Avocado asleep so everyone can have some./ Avocado gets skunked. Thankfully, Lucas helps her laugh at the situation./ Lucas has to convince Arlo that the garden hose isn't a snake.

title: #ConoceAGuepardo
description: Barbara Minerva está super celosa de la "pequeña señorita perfecta" Diana Prince. Pero cuando usa un antiguo artefacto de la colección de su padre para lanzar una maldición contra Diana, la maldición se vuelve en su contra.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Chloe and Ice Bear
description: On a day out with just Ice Bear, Chloe realizes Ice Bear only runs errands for his brothers. Determined to show him a fun day in the city, Chloe promises to help Ice Bear have a good time, even if it means staying  in a museum after it closes.

title: The Question
description: Steven shows some city slicker gems how the cowboys lived.

title: Prickly Pals/A Sting in the Tale/Tongue Twister
description: When Arlo plays too rough, Lucas forms a new friendship with a cactus./ Maizie accidentally stings Lucas's butt. This is a shock to them both, but Maizie takes it the hardest./ When Bodhi's tongue gets hurt, it's up to Dr. Lucas to help.

title: Fun Dungeon Face Off
description: Clarence's Mom treats Clarence, Jeff and Sumo to an afternoon at Rough Riders Chicken, a fast food restaurant with a play emporium. When Clarence and Sumo steal Jeff's fries, Jeff is forced to confront his germ phobias head-on in the restaurant's seemingly unsanitary play area.

title: Shun and Lightning/Premonition of a Storm
description: Shun and Lightning: Shun and Lightning are on the hunt for a rare Tumpee, when they run into McQ! With all the devices related crimes happening in Los Volmos, Shun decides to investigate to try to get to the bottom of McQ's nefarious dealings./Premonition of a Storm: After a run in with McQ, Shun and Lightning find themselves in a little bit trouble. They're trapped!  Tied up with no Bakugan to help them escape, and no one knows their whereabouts. It will take some big help to help them get out of this mess.

title: La Inteligencia
description: La tecnología alcanza el nivel de la inteligencia humana, y luego se vuelve disfuncional cuando imita sus defectos.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Follow that Space Cab!
description: While Superman escorts his prisoner Mr. Mind between planets, he is attacked by Lobo who wants to collect a reward on Mind. Temporarily powered-down, Superman seeks Space Cabbie's help to get away from Lobo.

title: Noche de Pelicula
description: Llegó la Noche de las Películas, y a los Titanes les cuesta decidir a quién le toca elegir qué película mirar.

title: Diente de Zombi
description: Cuando el evento favorito de Gwen, el Desfile de los Zombies, cae el mismo día que el día de pesadilla de Beth, la revisión con el dentista, las dos chicas encuentran un modo de ayudarse entre sí.

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: Familiar
description: With many changes going on in his life, Steven tries to find his place in the world.

title: El Fundador
description: Papá desata un caos en el edificio Chanax cuando lo confunden con el presidente de la empresa, desaparecido hace tiempo. Mamá y un empleado insatisfecho deben salvar a todos de las ideas peligrosas de Richard.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: #MeetTheCheetah
description: Barbara Minerva is super-jealous of  "little Miss Perfect" Diana Prince. But when she uses an ancient artifact from her dad's collection to place a curse on Diana, it turns out that Diana's not the one who's cursed. It's Barbara.

title: Man Up 2: Still Man-ing
description: When someone steals all the water in Townsville, it's up to the girls to race through the Townsville Wastelands to get it back.

title: Maestro Detective
description: Robin usa sus destrezas como maestro detective para descubrir lo que les sucedió a los animales que viven fuera de la Torre de los Titanes.

title: RV Olympics
description: Pizza Steve and Mr. Gus compete in the RV Olympics.

title: Ken 10
description: We're back in the future with Ben 10K, and this time he has a son, Ken. On Ken's tenth birthday, Ben gives him his very own Omnitrix. Ben must come to learn to trust Ken with the power of the Omnitrix. Along the way, Ken befriends a kid named Devlin. Devlin turns out to be Kevin 11's son and was merely using Ken so he could break his dad out of the Null Void. Ben 10K and Ken then team up to take down Kevin 11. As for Devlin, he comes to realize his dad is a jerk, and realizes the error of his ways. He's able to redeem himself, proving he's a good kid and joining forces with "Team Tennyson."

title: Picture Perfect Park Party/Sun Block
description: Hero Celebration Day is finishing with a slideshow of everyday heroes, that is, until the projector screen rips./Pretty Big City is cooling off with an ice slide in the park, but the situation gets slippery when the slide starts melting.

title: Capture The Flag Part I
description: When mysterious circumstances cause issues at the Trading Tree, Craig tries to save the day!

title: We Baby Bears Official Trailer: New Series
description: These baby bears are searching for a brand new home, and they're off to fantastical worlds and new adventures along the way. Watch the official trailer for We Baby Bears, the brand new show from the creators of We Bare Bears, coming to Cartoon Network in 2022.

title: Ben 4 Good Buddy
description: Out on a desert highway, a group of modern day highway pirates hijack the Rustbucket, trick it out and use it in a daring robbery. And while Ben and Gwen are at first glad to get rid of that "bucket of bolts", they come to realize the Rustbucket is "a part of the family." In the end our trio heroes get Max's beloved "ride" back and bring down these pirates once and for all.

title: Lady Rainicorn of the Crystal Dimension
description: Jake's son TV finds a hidden box and draws the attention of a super cool Rainicorn named Lee.

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: #AdventuresInBunnysitting
description: Zee asks Kara to look after her two magical bunnies, which quickly start to multiply, wreaking havoc all across Metropolis.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Reunited
description: Steven brings everyone together for a special reunion.

title: The Vegging
description: Gumball and Darwin want to have a lazy day on the sofa, and have come up with various tricks to stop themselves having to move. Gradually more and more people arrive, seemingly to get them to move, until finally they realize that if they have to move, they'll do it in the laziest way possible.

title: Azulejo
description: Steven cuestiona los motivos de una misteriosa fusión que de repente se presenta en su casa.

title: Double Trouble
description: Pocoyo wants to play ball but Pato is stubborn: he wants to play on the see-saw. Elly turns up so Pocoyo goes to play catch with her. Pato's left on his own. And the see-saw is no fun on your own. But he has an idea. He gets a machine and makes a copy of himself, a clone. The clone likes playing for a while but when they both want to play with the same toy car, they fall out. So Pato makes another Pato. Every time he makes a new Pato, something goes wrong, because the Patos all want the same thing and are as stubborn as each other. Finally, one of the clone Patos clones itself and soon there are crowds of Patos rampaging all around the place. Pocoyo and Elly to the rescue! They turn off the machine and all the copy Patos disappear. Phewy. To end, Pato plays ball.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: It's Time
description: Mordecai and Rigby get in a fight over Margaret, and Mordecai sends them traveling through time by destroying all the clocks.

title: Mother's Day
description: Gumball, Darwin and Anais need to find the perfect Mother's Day gift. Will it be a cute card, a thoughtful painting or something entirely different? Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Lost in the Supermarket
description: During a trip to the supermarket with his mom, Clarence discovers produce adventure and coupon intrigue in aisle five...and every other aisle.

title: Delivery Effect
description: Unikitty and gang have ordered some delicious Thai food for dinner.  Unfortunately the wait for the delivery is proving too much, time itself seems to have slowed down. In an effort to get the food their faster the gang utilizes Dr. Fox's time machine, which causes big problems and really hurts Father Time's feelings.

title: And Then There Were None
description: Vilgax and Eon team up to wipe out every Ben in every dimension!

title: Toddler Titans...Yay!
description: Control Freak thinks the Titans' humor is too juvenile for their time-slot, so he ages them down to a preschool show.

title: #LaCubetaDeBurritos
description: A Babs le encanta su trabajo en el restaurante de comida rápida "La Cubeta de Burritos" , pero a su jefe, que está harto de que ella siempre llegue tarde y de su enorme dispersión, le encantaría encontrar cualquier excusa para despedirla. Cuando se produce un robo a un banco que está enfrente de su trabajo, Babs no puede decidir si encarnar su papel de superheroína o el de empleada obediente de La Cubeta. Pero ¿será capaz de salvar a todos y conservar su empleo justo a tiempo?
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Paseo en Buggy
description: Después de ganar un cinturón como campeón de Luchadores de Sumo, Ben regresa al Rustbucket y encuentra su premio en los brazos de Kevin. Pero cuando su rival secuestra el Rustbuggy, inuestro héroe no debe detenerse ante nada para recuperar lo que le pertenece legítimamente!

title: Salad Salsa
description: Mei, Ella, animals cook a delicious salad using local vegetables

title: A Yoorg Awakening
description: Funshine's jokes unwittingly hurt the feelings of a strange Rock Giant. Disturbed from its slumber, the usually benign creature inadvertently creates havoc for the Whiffles until Funshine calms it by apologizing.

title: Abate and Switch
description: When the JLA tries to stop the Brothers Djinn, the ghoulish trio are able to direct spells on our heroes by saying their names forcing them to disguise themselves as each other in order to foil the spells.

title: The Second Stage Begins/Mechanoids Attack!
description: The Second Stage Begins: With half of the brawlers eliminated, the second stage of the Bakugan Battle league begins. This round will be a timed race to the finish, with all kinds of tricks and traps that will slow down even the best brawlers./Mechanoids Attack!: Mechanoids have crashed the second stage of the Bakugan Battle League, causing all kinds of havoc. The Awesome Brawlers will now have to race against the clock, battling competitors and mechanoids if they want to make it through this round.

title: Lil Noodle
description: Apple and Onion must remain legit enough to be in their favorite rapper's music video.

title: No puedo regresar
description: Ronaldo divisa algo misterioso en la luna, y Steven sale a investigar.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: Manzana Mandona
description: Manzana queda a cargo de la Tienda de Dolar por primera vez.

title: Don't Look
description: At the top of Dead Mountain, Finn discovers a treasure that comes with a terrible price.

title: Shadow
description: Bing is playing shadow tag with Flop, but what will happen when the clouds come?

title: En la Oscuridad
description: La princesa Vania revela una entrada secreta que conduce a una mina subterránea bajo Shintaro donde se guardan los oscuros secretos de la ciudad.

title: Superhero Feud
description: Control Freak pits the Titans against the DC Superhero Girls to determine who is the best team in the universe.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Pet Shop
description: Pet Shop tells the tale of where the Baby Bears once lived, and after a run-in with a video crew shooting a Sarah McLachlan-type animal adoption video, almost seized an opportunity to find a home separated from each other.

title: Apple's Focus
description: Apple decides to help Onion achieve his dream of competing on a baking show.

title: Roll Chickens, Roll!/Ramp Up, Up, And Away
description: Farmer MacBarm is hosting the Sunny Field Farm Chicken Roll, but the race gets off to a slow start when the chickens don't roll./Ranger Nat can't wait to see Pinecone's Comet, that is, until his telescope falls to the bottom of a cliff.

title: Poczilla
description: Pocoyo and Pato are playing at being terrifying giant monsters, like the sort of monsters they've seen in their comics. They find a toy city and enjoy being like Godzilla and King Kong. They don't notice that the little toys who live in the city are scared and that they're all running away in terror as Pocoyo and Pato destroy their toy city. The audience tells Pocoyo and Pato to stop. Once Pocoyo and Pato realize what's been going on they repair the damage and make a wonderful funfair for the little toys.

title: Juego Terminado
description: Unagami entra al mundo real y aterroriza a la ciudad de Ninjago mientras Jay, Zane y Pixal intentan evitar el desastre reuniendo a Unagami con Dyer.

title: Cartas para Lars
description: Steven escribe sobre las últimas novedades de Ciudad Playa.

title: Una Idea Huev-Xtremadamente Mala
description: Esperando "iluminar su día", Izzy y Owen decoran la silla huevo de Gwe. Pero cuando termina en un museo regentado por pollos rabiosos, deben rescatarla antes de que Gwen destruya la guardería en un berrinche de inusitada oscuridad.

title: Cuatro por Cuatro
description: Durante su visita a Ciudad Gemelos, Ben y Gwen se inscriben en una competencia de laser-tag. Pero cuando Ben se une a Kevin, los dos deben superar sus diferencias si quieren terminar en la cima.

title: Viral Spiral
description: When the Amoeba Boys wreak havoc on the internet, Bubbles has to hack her sisters in to stop them.

title: Mock 10
description: Ben, Kevin and La Grange find themselves stuck 'outside of time' after the latter hijacks a supersonic train with a faulty engine, forcing the trio to team up and slow down.

title: La Pocion
description: Gumball y Darwin usan una poción mágica para encoger a Héctor.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: El Tonto
description: Darwin termina en la sala de detención con el Chico Bomba, que decide convertir a Darwin en su nuevo blanco. Sin embargo, el ataque se vuelve en su contra cuando Darwin le arruina la vida.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Adventurers
description: Because Mush-Mush, Chep and Lilit are always up to new adventures, Bolly has dubbed them The Adventurers. Flattered, our friends invite Bolly to choose his challenge to become an Adventurer too. Bolly will have to be the first Mushable to set foot somewhere. Mushton being crowded, Mush-Mush suggests they find an island, somewhere on the giant lake.

title: La Zona
description: A Unikitty le cuesta mantener la calma cuando juega a videojuegos y entra en La Zona, a diferencia de Puppycorn, su hermano menor. Pero un repentino accidente de laboratorio destroza su consola y ahora, para su sorpresa, el castillo se bloquea como un videojuego del mundo real, icon sus amigos como jugadores! ¿Podrá Unikitty salvar a sus amigos y dominar La Zona antes de que termine el juego?

title: Modern-ish Stone Age Family
description: The Bears are invited to live with a family of cavemen but things get rocky when the bears teach the family about television.

title: An Egg-stremely Bad Idea
description: Hoping to 'brighten her day', Izzy and Owen pimp out Gwen's egg chair. But when it ends up in a museum run by angry chickens, they must retrieve it before Gwen destroys the daycare in a temper tantrum of unspeakable darkness.

title: Ready to Rumble
description: After Ben thinks he's broken Gwen's computer, he sneaks off and enters an "ultimate wrestling competition" to win enough money to buy her a new one. On the mat as Fourarms, he becomes an instant celebrity hit with the fans and ends up going up against a tandem of odd looking brothers with special mutant-like powers. Initially adversaries, Ben and the brothers become allies when Ben discovers the brothers are beholden to a powerful mob boss. Ben helps the brothers defeat the mob boss and his henchmen, and in the end realizes Gwen's computer was never really broken.

title: Guidance
description: Amethyst has been helping Little Homeschool Gems find jobs on the boardwalk, but Steven isn't sure about her approach.

title: Atrapados en el paraiso
description: Unikitty y la banda aterrizaron de emergencia en una isla fabulosa. Todo es muy bonito y nadie quiere irse hasta que Richard los convence de que tienen que volver al Reino y asumir sus responsabilidades. Por desgracia, alguien sabotea cada intento de escapar de la isla. Ahora deben encontrar al culpable para asegurar su regreso a casa.

title: Legs from Here to Homeworld
description: Steven travels to visit family.

title: Huelga por el Botin
description: Mientras Phil y el abuelo Max afinan el Omni-Copter, Ben, inquieto, saca el Rustbuggy de la carretera. Pero cuando de repente es capturado por Tetrax, nuestro héroe no solo debe escapar, sino también evitar la ira de los traicioneros Kraab y SeiSeis.

title: Smash House
description: The Looney Builders learn that Taz accidentally destroyed his house, so they set out to build him a new one that's smash-proof.

title: Ello Gov'nor
description: After watching a scary movie about a British Taxi, the guys have to help Rigby overcome his fears.

title: Prank War
description: When Master Frown starts a prank war with UniKingdom, the friends are ready to strike back. But Unikitty doesn't really understand pranks, thinking they're too mean. Can the friends help Unikitty comprehend a proper goof and win the prank war with Frown? Or will they be forced to suffer his tricks without retaliation and admit defeat?

title: Safety First
description: Concerned about Puppycorn's propensity to hurt himself constantly, the gang places him into Richard's old Safety Suit. The suit does indeed keep him safe, but when Puppycorn purposefully puts himself in danger the suit goes into lock down, and won't allow him to move. Now the gang must figure out a way to get him out of the Safety Suit.

title: Ahora nos estamos separando
description: Perla cuenta una historia.

title: Blast Off Bugs
description: Baby Bugs tries to realize his dream of traveling to the moon while the Baby Looney Tunes are on a space museum visit.

title: Dizzy
description: M and R help Pops get over his fear of public speaking.

title: El Elegido
description: Tobías intenta ser el mejor amigo de Gumball.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: #HateTriangle
description: When Hal's ex-girlfriend shows up at the Metropolis High homecoming game and goes love-ballistic as the villain Star Sapphire, Jessica begins to second-guess her own nonviolent tactics.

title: Monster Mystery
description: Pocoyo makes a monster mask out of an old box. When he fails to scare Elly and Pato, he kicks the box out of the way in frustration. The box lands on Sleepy Bird who can't get out of it. She flies close to Pocoyo to ask for help but he and his friends are terrified. A chase ensues. Finally Baby Bird works it out. It was Sleepy Bird all along. The friends all have a monster mash party together at the end.

title: Los Padres
description: Nicole se reconcilia con sus padres.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Tweety-Go-Round
description: Tweety leads The Looney Builders in building a new merry-go-round at the park for the kids. His crane breaks down and his small size affects his ability to contribute to the build.

title: Dinosaur Day
description: Pizza Steve's jealousy ruins Uncle Grandpa's Dinosaur Day celebration for Mr. Gus.

title: El Peor Rescate de la Historia
description: Los Ninjas intentan rescatar a Cole, pero las discusiones entre prisioneros alertan al Hechicero Calavera, y hace prisioneros a los otros Ninjas.

title: Capture The Flag Part V
description: It all comes down to this, the fate of the Creek is at stake!

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Little Homeschool
description: Welcome to Little Homeschool, a place on earth where Gems from all over the universe can come learn how to live together peacefully! But there's one Gem who refuses to attend.

title: Demasiados Unikitties
description: Unikitty llega a la conclusión de que todo el mundo sería mucho más feliz si pensara como ella, iy tal vez pueda lograrlo con la ayuda de la Dra. Fox! Unikitty copia sus ondas cerebrales en todos sus amigos y los Unikittyfica, para que todos puedan ser siempre positivos. Pero pronto, Unikitty se da cuenta de que puede haber un exceso de "buena princesa".

title: El Menti-Ranosaurio
description: Owen finge ser el dinosaurio mascota de Izzy después de hacerle creer que lo sacó del patio de la escuela.

title: The Magical Box
description: After Grizz, Panda and Ice Bear receive a special box, the brothers discover its magical ability to transport them anywhere in the universe.

title: Tote Life
description: When a hipster grocery store clerk shames the Bears for asking for plastic grocery bags, the Bears realize that eco-friendly tote bags are their way of gaining acceptance amongst the progressive people of the Bay Area. But in their effort to gain popularity, the Bears let the culture of tote bags take over their lives.

title: Guerra de Bromas
description: Cuando Master Frown comienza una guerra de bromas con el Unireino, los amigos están listos para contraatacar. Pero Unikitty no entiende bien las bromas, y piensa que tienen demasiada maldad. ¿Pueden los amigos ayudar a Unikitty a comprender una buena broma y ganar la guerra contra Frown? ¿O se verán obligados a sufrir sus bromas sin represalias y admitir la derrota?

title: Fun Proof
description: Apple and Onion want to become this week's "Most Fun People".

title: Mo Job/Pet Feud
description: Mo Job: Princess hires Mojo to devise the perfect plan to destroy the girls, who are quite shocked when they find Princess has powers equal to their own./Pet Feud: The Professor creates the perfect little pet. But there's only one catch: he can only be fed once a day. When the girls each feed him, they find that their sweet little friend has become a wild beast!

title: The Two Blades
description: In order to escape the Skull Sorcerer's chain-gang, the ninja must convince the Munce and Geckles to put aside their distrust and work together… by promising them something they may not be able to deliver -- The Blades of Deliverance!

title: Bluebird
description: Steven questions the motives of a mysterious fusion that suddenly shows up at his house.

title: Volleyball
description: Steven is determined to help Pink Diamond's original Pearl heal the scar on her face.

title: Shintaro
description: Los Ninjas están invitados a asistir a la fiesta de cumpleaños de la princesa Vania en la ciudad de Shintaro. Llevan al Maestro Wu que está deprimido.

title: Xingo's World
description: Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max are on the road again and are supposed to be taking in the beautiful sights, but Ben refuses to put his video games away. Only the unexpected return of Xingo can spur him into action and teach him that the real world is just as important as any virtual one!

title: Robo-Maestra
description: Cuando una maestra suplente reemplaza a Chef, Duncan cree que será el mejor día de la historia. Se equivoca.

title: Lazer Tag
description: When the Score creeper traps Unikitty and the gang in his laser tag arena the gang must defeat the house team or be imprisoned forever.

title: Pretty Great Day with a Girl
description: Clarence and Amy, a unique girl from down the street, bond over a hunt for a monster-sized rock called an "erratic."

title: El Chupacabro
description: El equipo Tennyson descubre que las cabras de una pequeña aldea están siendo aterrorizadas por el legendario Chupacabra. Pero cuando Ben se da cuenta de que en realidad se trata del Dr. Ánimo, nuestro héroe debe frustrar al malvado médico.

title: Gato de laboratorio
description: La Dra. Fox necesita Unikitty y Puppycorn como voluntarios para ser sus ratas de laboratorio, idigo, asistentes de investigación en un nuevo y audaz experimento que los lanzará al espacio! Pero a medida que la misión se vuelve más peligrosa, la Dra. Fox se ve obligada a elegir entre el avance científico de sus sueños y volver a ver a sus amigos.

title: It's a Mad, Mad, Mad Ben World Part 1
description: Alternate dimensions, duplicate Bens and villains from throughout time and space! Just another day in Bellwood.

title: Sir Topham Hatt's Hat
description: When Sir Topham Hatt's Hat blows away in the wind before making an important announcement, Thomas and his friends race around Sodor, trying to catch it. The Hat remains out of reach until they learn to work together.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The Rival
description: The Wattersons look back on Anais' first days in the Watterson house. Gumball and Darwin quickly find themselves up an opponent who is able to outsmart them at every turn.

title: Odd Bubbles Out
description: When Donny the Unicorn visits, Bubbles becomes jealous of his new friend.

title: #Beeline
description: Cuando tropieza con un malvado complot para hacer explotar un puente de la ciudad, Bumblebee se espanta y acude a sus amigas para que derroten a los malhechores. Pero cuando todas sus super amigas están ocupadas, Bumblebee debe buscar cada gramo de coraje en ella para hacer frente a la situación, a pesar de ser la más pequeña del grupo.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: #Beeline
description: When she stumbles across a villainous plot to blow up a bridge, Bumblebee shies from the challenge of taking on the baddies and reaches out to her friends. But when the other heroes are all indisposed, it'll take every ounce of courage Bumblebee has to rise to the occasion … despite being the smallest of the bunch.

title: La Leccion
description: Gumball y Darwin se hacen cargo de los trabajos de Larry durante 5 minutos y se dan cuenta de lo desagradable que son.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Los Vegetales
description: Gumball y Darwin solo quieren holgazanear todo el día, pero terminan teniendo que salvar al resto de la familia.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Into the Dark
description: When Cole investigates a mysterious visitor, the ninja aren't sure what to believe. Cole is frustrated with this lack of team support, until Princess Vania reveals a secret entrance that leads to an underground mine beneath Shintaro - where the city's dark secrets are held.

title: Nia's Surprising Surprise
description: Nia is planning a big party to celebrate the anniversary of her arrival on Sodor, but she finds that her friends don't remember her anniversary and are too busy to even talk about it.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Game Over
description: Unagami breaks into the real world and terrorizes Ninjago City while Jay, Zane and Pixal attempt to prevent disaster by reuniting Unagami with his creator, Milton Dyer.

title: Whale Spotting
description: In order to see a rare whale, Apple and Onion have to become members of an exclusive club, but one of them doesn't quite have the chops.

title: It's a Mad, Mad, Mad Ben World Part 2
description: Ben and Dr. Psychobos become reluctant allies in a parallel-dimension maelstrom.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Shintaro
description: The ninja are invited to attend the birthday party of Princess Vania, in the distant Kingdom of Shintaro. They depart, bringing along Master Wu, unaware that he is feeling his age…

title: Fiesta de cumpleanos
description: Master Frown, el habitante más pesimista del reino, se roba el deseo de cumpleaños de Puppycorn. Para recuperarlo, Unikitty y Puppycorn tendrán que aventurarse en la tierra más deprimente de la historia: iFrown Town! ¿Conseguirán recuperar el deseo de cumpleaños de manos de Frown antes de que su deseo (y todos los deseos) desaparezcan para siempre?

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Alien X-Tinction
description: When the Tennysons are attacked by a villainous, dimension-hopping Omni-alien known only as Alien X, they soon meet a parallel universe version of Max who opens the door to hosting multiple Bens and Gwens, forming an alien hero army to combat this threat.

title: The Wheel Deal
description: Everyone's excited about a grand bicycle outing through the park, everyone except Tweety whose little legs don't quite reach the pedals. Frustrated after riding on the back of Floyd's bicycle while everyone else has fun, Tweety is ready to go home.

title: Gyranoid of the Future
description: Apple and Onion are dead set on riding Gyranoid of the Future, the craziest roller coaster at the carnival.

title: Uncle Melvins
description: Legendary rock band, the Melvins, team up with Uncle Grandpa to help a young girl who wants to win her school's talent show.

title: Here I Go
description: Bing and Pando find a new slide at the playground, but it's very high. Will Bing be able to go down the slide?

title: Players of the Lost Park
description: When Team Tennyson visits Raspberry Park for some R & R, they get more than they bargained for. What they think are innocent games of chance are a revenge plot by Zombozo to steal the Rustbuggy and rob Team Tennyson!

title: Bubbles of the Opera
description: When Bubbles gets a bad school photo, it sends her into an existential tailspin of darkness.

title: Clarence's Millions
description: When Clarence realizes the classroom "buddy star" system is leaving some kids behind, he creates his own form of currency called "Clarence Dollars." The new reward system promptly turns the entire school upside down.

title: La seguridad es primero
description: Preocupados por la propensión de Perricornio a lastimarse constantemente, la banda le coloca el viejo traje de seguridad de Richard. El traje lo mantiene a salvo, pero cuando Perricornio se pone en peligro a propósito, el traje se bloquea y le impide moverse. Ahora la banda debe encontrar la manera de sacarlo del traje de seguridad.

title: Power Outage
description: A ghoul known as Calythos possesses the Parasite in order to drain the Justice League of its powers and use that stolen strength to open a massive volcano.

title: Trapped in Paradise
description: Unikitty and the gang have crashed on a fabulous island. It's really nice and no one wants to leave until Richard convinces them that they need to return to the Kingdom and deal with their responsibilities. Unfortunately every attempt to escape the island is sabotaged. Now they must find the culprit to ensure their return home.

title: Imaginary Fiend/Cootie Gras
description: Imaginary Fiend: The new boy in school has a special friend nobody else can see. When this imaginary friend begins destroying the class, the girls must imagine how to stop him./Cootie Gras: Mojo observes that everyone is staying away from little Harry Pitt because he has cooties. So Mojo concocts a plan to keep the girls away by using this cootie-covered boy as bait.

title: #BurritoBucket
description: Babs loves her job at fast food restaurant Burrito Bucket, but her boss, who's fed up with her chronic lateness and bad case of scatterbrain, would love any excuse to fire her. When a bank robbery breaks out right across the street from work, Babs is torn between her role as a superhero and dutiful Burrito Bucket employee. Will she be able to save the day and keep her job all in the nick of time?

title: Capture The Flag Part II
description: The Creek gets help from an unlikely friend.

title: Bakugan Battle League, Tokyo Edition/Battle Royal
description: Bakugan Battle League, Tokyo Edition: It's the start of the Bakugan Battle League - Toyko edition! The first round will be a Battle Royale style competition, where only half the competitors will make it through to the next round. Along with the Awesome brawlers the field of competitors is filled with familiar friends and foes./Battle Royal: The first round of the Bakugan Battle League - Tokyo edition continues. The Awesome Brawler's and their Bakugan battle their way through the challenge and face off against tough competitors.

title: Capture The Flag Part IV
description: Craig puts a plan into motion to save the Creek.

title: The One
description: Gumball and Darwin are joking around, but when Tobias joins in and makes fun of Gumball, he's incredibly offended. They explain to Tobias that to make those jokes he'd need to be higher on Gumball's friend list. They think that's the end of it, but Tobias is after that number one spot.

title: Farewell Friends
description: Pato is leaving: he's packed his bags, he's said goodbye to his room and all his things. He's had one last sniff of his favorite flowers and said goodbye to Caterpillar, Alien, Baby Bird and Sleepy Bird. And there's the plane he's leaving in…! One last chance to say good bye. Good bye Pato!!! Everyone is waving and saying goodbye. Pato gets in the plane. One last wave. It's so sad!!! The plane goes in a circle one super-quick time and then Pato's home again. Hooray. Time for a welcome home party - and for someone else to have a go!

title: Charlie and the Snake
description: Charlie is a solo guy who, like the Bears, would love to find a place for himself in the world. In an effort to do so, Charlie throws a party, but ends up going on an adventure with the unlikeliest of animals, a wild snake.

title: Jerky Jasper
description: Uncle Grandpa goes to great lengths to meet Pizza Steve's imaginary friend.

title: Consejos
description: Amatista ha estado ayudando a las Gemas de Pequeña Escuela Madre a encontrar trabajo, pero Steven no está seguro de su enfoque.

title: Broke His Crown
description: When Ice King's magic crown goes haywire, Marceline and Princess Bubblegum resort to extreme measures to help him.

title: Ola de Calor
description: Manzana y Cebollín tratan de esparcir alegría durante una ola de calor en toda la ciudad.

title: Boo-Dunnit
description: When the box goes missing at a haunted mansion, the Bears play detective to help uncover the thief.

title: Papel de Bano Bebecin
description: Manzana necesita conseguir la provisión del papel higiénico que usaría en toda su vida para terminar su escultura de arte moderno.

title: Nobody's Perfect
description: When Cheer makes some simple mistakes, she begins to lose confidence in her piloting skills and herself. The self-doubt becomes so severe, she decides to step away from her role as pilot of the Cloudseeker. But the Team needs her, the Whiffles need her, and she must regain her self-confidence so they can stop Bluster's latest nefarious scheme.

title: Ancestor Act
description: When Gumball's sister Anais researches the Watterson family tree, she uncovers a long history of nonsense. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Worst Rescue Ever
description: The ninja attempt to rescue Cole, but the bickering of his fellow prisoners, the Geckles and Munce, alerts the Skull Sorcerer, and soon the ninja are prisoners too.

title: Baby Mouth
description: In order to find out about his family history, Robin takes a DNA test and discovers he's from Babylon.

title: I Am a Sword
description: Finn starts having guilt nightmares about his missing Finn Sword but are the nightmares real?

title: El Rival
description: Volvemos a la época en la que Anaís era una bebé recién nacida, y los celos de Gumball y Darwin desatan una guerra de bebés.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Sucker
description: Gumball spends the day with Bomb Kid, who has decided Gumball is the perfect target for him and his friends to play pranks on. However he soon learns that Gumball is so gullible that pranks bounce off him.
